user.intro:
Hey everyone! I'm Ryan, a current Contrary VP (still the best decision I've made) at _Duke University_ studying CS and more broadly how people make decisions.

• I'm _born in Taipei_ but can usually be found in NC/SF, and also spent summers in LA/Seattle/Boston. Always happy to grab food if anyone's in town, and talk about Asia/Greater China vs the US!
